version_description: Wardriving database registration fix.

Become social and crowd sharing.
New robots for password calculation.
New dictionaries from 2005 up to 2016.
New WiFi Map feature with Free WiFi Hotspots.
Introducing WODSPOTS, community WiFi Hotspots.
New Free WiFi Hotspots databases.

Minor bugs fixes
New robots for TotalPlay and Huawei-HG8245

Wireless Passwords From Airports And Lounges Around The World.
iOS 10 support and UI changes and fixes.
English, Spanish (Es-Es), Spanish (ES-Mex), Chinese (Simplified) and Indonesian.

Scan for nearby WiFi or WodSpots and connect to them.
We are celebrating #iWepPRO 8th anniversary and dictionaries and WodSpots access are free! For limited time only.

New USA and Germany supported routers added.
Stability issues and minor bugs fixed.
Japan WodSpots city names issue fixed.
Added Youtube link to video tutorials and Twitter link for support.

Added Support for more world wide routers
iOS 10.2.1 fixes

Follow instructions in the app notifications for WiFi connection in the WiFi hotspots around you.
Fix location issues with WodSpots.
Added tracking for 0 count in WodSpots.
Dictionaries are back, so you can use them when you are out of internet, offline mode.

- Password tap crash for some devices in the main tableView has been fixed. Now you can select a password without crash.
- Improvements in WiFi WodSpots background loading.
- Dictionaries are back again for offline calculation.
- Added nice blue color to the UI and bottom tab bar.

We have made big changes to the core of the app, that's why we have set the version to 10.x. Stay tuned for a batery of sustancial changes. We are trying to get rid with the bugs some users are getting in some countries, now, we have added a crash report tool, so we can figure out what is going wrong if you find any problem with the app.
We have tried to fix all the bugs we have been reported about, so app performance is already improved. But we are fighting for the 0 crash reports!

In this version we are bringing fixes to the main bugs found in the last version:
· Main view bug fix when a network is selected.
· In App Purchase tap button fix when selecting one product.
· Main view bug fix when the table data is reloaded.
Added 2017 Dictionary for free just following us in twitter, stay tuned with the last #iWepPRO news and connect with other WodSpots community members.
